abstract: With investors already worried about the fiscal cliff, there's another wild card that will factor into the debates in Washington: the debt ceiling. | President Obama may be well positioned to push for changes in housing policy. | Kayak Software is being bought by Priceline.com for $1.8 billion in cash and stock. | Groupon is still having difficulty making money.
